ps://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/3/73511D14CCF6B991476F7D822968D2A7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Tuck Box - Christmas Bells</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Christmas Bells</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Festive Christmas Ribbon and Bells design Tuck Box</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/B/9B70986AD18A8B5665127D0501085E02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Tuck Box - Blue Ink Birthday</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blue Ink Birthday</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Blue gradients with balloons and Happy Birthday design Tuck Box</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Tuck Box – Large - Stock Designs. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">2005-LT</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>13 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">250</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}